# Test: Load map09 and perform basic gameplay
#
# Usage:
#   ./DoomIIRPG --game doom2rpg --map map09.bin --script Testing/test_map09.script --seed 1337 --headless
#   ./DoomIIRPG --game doom2rpg --map map09.bin --script Testing/test_map09.script --seed 1337
#
# Note: --map takes a .bin filename (e.g. map09.bin), not a bare name.
# With --map, the game skips intro/character selection and loads the map directly.

